{"id": 6828, "title": "Ticket #6828: Make package version accessible from condor_version", "description": "<blockquote>\nWe have a request to provide the package version (8.8.0-1) available. Note the \"-1\", we have occasionally had a \"-2\" release.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2018-Nov-20 09:24:05 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\nThe plan is augment the conversion output as follows for packaged builds (RPMs and DEBs):\n\n<p></p><div class=\"verbatim\">\n<pre>$CondorVersion: 8.4.4 Feb 03 2016 BuildID: 355883 PackageID: 8.4.4-1 $\n$CondorPlatform: x86_64_RedHat6 $\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Tarball and Windows builds will omit the PackageID in the output.\n\n</p><p></p><hr/>\n<em>2018-Dec-11 14:33:28 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>This change looks good.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Nov-21 12:14</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/4a9050eb5e18c6a33d13c8d0ce9c0fbc0fb04daf\">[55800]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6828\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6828'); return false;\" title=\"Make package version accessible from condor_version\">#6828</a></span>) Drip dist tag from Package ID  (By Tim Theisen )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Nov-21 12:09</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7676e6e2d65680b76b680106d725e395d6036e3c\">[55799]</a></span>: Remove extra quot